Interview with the developer of Looping

<p>
An interview with the original author of Video Games GmbH's "Looping" arcade game is available on this
site, thanks to Corrado Tomaselli and Antonio Gerli.  Head on over to the 
<a href="http://mamedev.org/roms/looping/looping-interview.html">English translation</a> 
of the interview, or the original 
<a href="http://mamedev.org/roms/looping/looping-intervista.html">Italian language version</a>.
</p>
<p>
Looping is available as a ROM download for free, non-commercial use
<a href="http://mamedev.org/roms/looping">here</a>.
</p>
